        <item>
            <title>重出江湖</title>
            <link>http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_471459780100bqki.html</link>
            <description><![CDATA[<p CLASS="MsoNormal" STYLE="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">
找什么理由都不足以说明解释推脱搪塞失踪于江湖数月的理由，其实也没啥特殊的理由，忙吧，都忙，也不对，累吧，谁不累？！都累。绝对不是闲，闲着没来，哈哈，就别揭发我啦<img STYLE="WIDTH: 22px; HEIGHT: 22px" HEIGHT="19" SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/005.gif" WIDTH="20" /><img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/005.gif" /><img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/005.gif" />，就让我说了算一回吧，谁让我是老大呢<img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/016.gif" /><img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/016.gif" /><img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/016.gif" />，我没做“老大”很久哩，哈哈哈哈哈</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">~~</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">但即便是老大搞江湖失踪，还是有众多江湖好汉好女不懈支持<img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/027.gif" /><img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/027.gif" />，老大我在这双手抱拳给各路好友行礼了</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">~~~</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">一鞠躬，二鞠躬，三鞠躬<img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/002.gif" />，哈哈哈哈。</SPAN></P>
<p CLASS="MsoNormal"><span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">&nbsp;</SPAN></P>
<p CLASS="MsoNormal" STYLE="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">
对江湖来说，还有个特别的日子，成立已经三周年啦<img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/007.gif" /><img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/007.gif" />！时间真是好快啊！一路走来太多欢乐和感动，补发过往的照片，庆祝一下吧<img STYLE="WIDTH: 19px; HEIGHT: 19px" SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/030.gif" />。另外，今天是平安夜，相信有很多人都已经约好了饭局、酒局，一年下来能“名正言顺”喝大酒的日子不多，今儿就是一个，但一定要注意安全，寒冬出门注意保暖<img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/001.gif" /><img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/001.gif" />。鉴于今天出门的人太多，我就不掺和了，准备在家蜗居……</SPAN></P>
<p CLASS="MsoNormal" STYLE="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0">
&nbsp;</P>
<p CLASS="MsoNormal" STYLE="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">
<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static14.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/47145978h5eca999bca1d" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://static14.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/47145978h5eca999bca1d" /></A></SPAN></P>
<p CLASS="MsoNormal" STYLE="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">
<font STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312,楷体" COLOR="#000000">大伙都不知道，当时拍这些照片时都要喊1、2、3，用最快的速度抓照片，尽管阳光充足，但还是需要穿厚衣服。</FONT></SPAN></P>
<p CLASS="MsoNormal" STYLE="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0">
&nbsp;</P>
<p CLASS="MsoNormal" STYLE="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">
<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static8.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/47145978h5eca9a558ad7" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://static8.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/47145978h5eca9a558ad7" /></A></SPAN></P>
<p CLASS="MsoNormal" STYLE="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">
<font STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312,楷体">后面是佛罗伦萨的全景，让小纪拍人与自然，结果，没有自然，只有人，还美其曰：和谐<img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/033.gif" /><img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/033.gif" />……</FONT></SPAN></P>
<p CLASS="MsoNormal" STYLE="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0">
&nbsp;</P>
<p CLASS="MsoNormal" STYLE="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">
<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static11.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/47145978h5eca9ac06eda" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://static11.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/47145978h5eca9ac06eda" /></A></SPAN></P>
<p CLASS="MsoNormal" STYLE="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">
<font STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312,楷体">看见我的车了吧，<img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/006.gif" /><img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/006.gif" /><img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/006.gif" />帅吧？全木制作，绝对环保的老爷车！据说，要加上油，这车还真能跑~~真想弄一个回来……</FONT></SPAN></P>
<p CLASS="MsoNormal" STYLE="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0">
&nbsp;</P>
<p CLASS="MsoNormal" STYLE="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">
<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static8.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/47145978h5eca9be0f617" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://static8.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/47145978h5eca9be0f617" /></A></SPAN></P>
<p CLASS="MsoNormal" STYLE="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">
<font STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312,楷体">我们在法国尼斯的广场.暴晒的阳光能把皮肤烤焦了，只能用披肩抵挡一阵了</FONT></SPAN></P>
<p CLASS="MsoNormal" STYLE="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0">
&nbsp;</P>
<p CLASS="MsoNormal" STYLE="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">
<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static12.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/47145978h5eca9c97fb7b" TARGET="_blank"><img SRC="http://static12.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/47145978h5eca9c97fb7b" /></A></SPAN></P>
<p CLASS="MsoNormal" STYLE="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">
<font STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312,楷体">著名的圣彼得大教堂，感叹欧洲的建筑奢华不失细腻，连着走了好多天，脚疼，歇歇，享受午后的阳光，如人生一样，不要因为赶路而忘记了欣赏路边的风景。</FONT></SPAN></P>
<p CLASS="MsoNormal" STYLE="TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">
<font FACE="楷体_GB2312"><font STYLE="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">ps：感谢江湖好友的指正，最后那张照片确实是在梵蒂冈的圣彼得大教堂前拍的<img STYLE="WIDTH: 19px; HEIGHT: 19px" SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/018.gif" /><img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/018.gif" />。太多照片，一不小心就弄混淆了……嘿嘿，已经改过来啦！</FONT><img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/004.gif" /><img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/004.gif" /><img SRC="http://blogimg.sinajs.cn/images/control/face/004.gif" /></FONT></SPAN></P>]]></description>
