            <title>生命中的第一张专辑</title>
            <link>http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_471459780100a4gz.html</link>
            <description><![CDATA[<p>
<b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 22pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">生命中的第一张专辑</SPAN></B></P>
<p>&nbsp;</P>
<p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static16.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/471459784526c32d4b85f" TARGET="_blank"><img STYLE="WIDTH: 594px; HEIGHT: 244px" HEIGHT="257" SRC="http://static16.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/471459784526c32d4b85f" WIDTH="599" /></A></P>
<p><span STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14px">每一个人都是放下手头的工作，赶到发布会现场支持……只是静静坐在下面看着我舞台上的表现，然后又要匆匆忙忙地赶回自己的拍摄现场……看着每一个人投来的关心的目光，我却忍不住心生歉意……</FONT></SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">
<font STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14px">人的一生不能没有朋友，来自朋友的鼓励，让我幸福着、温暖着、也不禁潸然泪下，内心充满感激……</FONT></SPAN></P>
<p><font STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
朋友——是你一生的财富。</FONT></P>
<p>&nbsp;</P>
<p><span STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static13.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/471459784526c40a5ebfc" TARGET="_blank"><img STYLE="WIDTH: 445px; HEIGHT: 284px" HEIGHT="308" SRC="http://static13.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/471459784526c40a5ebfc" WIDTH="474" /></A></SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;<a HREF="http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static6.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/471459784526c3858cdd5" TARGET="_blank"><img STYLE="WIDTH: 448px; HEIGHT: 297px" HEIGHT="280" SRC="http://static6.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/471459784526c3858cdd5" WIDTH="423" /></A></SPAN></P>
<p><span STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <font STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14px">实在是找不到人都全的照片，上面的“最完整”大合影还是把两个好哥们落下了，特此再补发两张他们的特写。</FONT></SPAN><font STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14px">&nbsp;</FONT></P>
<p>&nbsp;</P>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
<span STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">
本老大发专辑了，这是我生命中的第一张专辑——《自</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" XML:LANG="EN-US">&amp;</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">己》。这几天正忙于专辑的发布和宣传，全国各地地跑，收到好多朋友的祝福和关心，大家也问我：为什么要叫《自</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" XML:LANG="EN-US">&amp;</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">己》呢？在这里并没有一个标准的概念，一定要让人去按照某个既定好的方向去理解。我这样觉得，一个人的一生是在寻找自己的一生，也许我们并没有真正地了解自己理解自己，也许你的某位朋友、某个同事</SPAN><span LANG="EN-US" STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" XML:LANG="EN-US">……</SPAN><span STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">会了解你多一些，而自己处在一个当局者的身份，在看待自己的时候可能存在着某些盲点。也许扫盲的过程正像制作这张专辑，酝酿了一年半之久的时间，融进了我很多的心血和心思，是想表达一个真实的、真诚的自己，与你分享。</SPAN></P>
<p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
<span STYLE="FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">
而今天我更想做自己、做好自己、认真做自己……</SPAN></P>]]></description>
